            class="- topic/topic concept/concept ">
		    <title class="- topic/title ">
			      <ph props="autonumber" class="- topic/ph ">16.205-3</ph> Limitations.</title>
		    <conbody class="- topic/body concept/conbody ">
			      <p class="- topic/p ">This contract type shall not be used unless-</p>
			      <ol id="d972e16" class="- topic/ol ">
				        <li class="- topic/li ">
					          <p id="d986e20" class="- topic/p ">
                  <ph props="autonumber" class="- topic/ph ">(a)</ph>
                  
                  
                  
                  
                  
                  
                  
                  
                  
                  
                  
						            Negotiations have established that-</p>
					          <ol id="d972e26" class="- topic/ol ">
						            <li class="- topic/li ">
							              <p id="d986e30" class="- topic/p ">
                        <ph props="autonumber" class="- topic/ph ">(1)</ph>
                        
                        
                        
                        
                        
                        
                        
                        
                        
                        
                        
								                The conditions for use of a firm-fixed-price contract are not present (see <xref href="FAR-i1104860.dita#i1104860"
                              base="i1104860"
                              outputclass="fm:ParaNumOnly"
                              class="- topic/xref ">16.202-2</xref>); and</p>
						            </li>
						            <li class="- topic/li ">
							              <p id="d986e42" class="- topic/p ">
                        <ph props="autonumber" class="- topic/ph ">(2)</ph>
                        
                        
                        
                        
                        
                        
                        
                        
                        
                        
                        
								                A fixed-price incentive contract would not be more appropriate;</p>
						            </li>
					          </ol>
				        </li>
				        <li class="- topic/li ">
					          <p id="d986e53" class="- topic/p ">
                  <ph props="autonumber" class="- topic/ph ">(b)</ph>
                  
                  
                  
                  
                  
                  
                  
                  
                  
                  
                  
						            The contractor’s accounting system is adequate for price redetermination;</p>
				        </li>
				        <li class="- topic/li ">
					          <p id="d986e62" class="- topic/p ">
                  <ph props="autonumber" class="- topic/ph ">(c)</ph>
                  
                  
                  
                  
                  
                  
                  
                  
                  
                  
                  
						            The prospective pricing periods can be made to conform with operation of the contractor’s accounting system; and</p>
				        </li>
				        <li class="- topic/li ">
					          <p id="d986e71" class="- topic/p ">
                  <ph props="autonumber" class="- topic/ph ">(d)</ph>
                  
                  
                  
                  
                  
                  
                  
                  
                  
                  
                  
						            There is reasonable assurance that price redetermination actions will take place promptly at the specified times.</p>
				        </li>
			      </ol>
		    </conbody>
